      { day: 'Day 10', title: 'Darchen → Return Journey Begins', desc: 'Begin the return drive toward Lhasa or continue onward travel. Many pilgrims take an extra day to revisit Lake Manasarovar for a ritual bath. Flight connections from Lhasa typically require an additional 2-3 days of driving.' },
