<Layout title="Mount Kailash Pilgrimage Guide 2026 — Complete Planning Resource | Kailash 2026" description="Comprehensive Mount Kailash pilgrimage guide: best time to visit, permits, physical preparation, packing list, altitude sickness prevention, accommodation, transport, and cost breakdown for the 2026 Horse Year kora.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
