        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-10 text-gray-500 text-sm">
        Have questions? <a href="/en/contact" class="text-kailash-gold underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-kailash-dark transition">Contact us</a> — we're here to help you prepare for the pilgrimage of a lifetime.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
